<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1470] index formats always compound</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1470</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seems like the index format is always compound now.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
